field.name: BeginString
field.description: Identifies beginning of new message and protocol version. ALWAYS FIRST FIELD IN MESSAGE

field.name: BodyLength
field.description: Message length; in bytes; forward to the CheckSum field. ALWAYS SECOND FIELD IN MESSAGE.

field.name: CheckSum
field.description: Three byte; simple checksum ("Checksum Calculation" for description). ALWAYS LAST FIELD IN MESSAGE with the trailing ; as the end-of-message delimiter. Always defined as three characters. (Always unencrypted)

field.name: MsgSeqNum
field.description: Integer message sequence number used for session management

field.name: SenderSubID
field.description: Sender Sub-Identifer Assigned value used to identify specific message originator (desk, trader, etc.)

field.name: SignatureLength
field.description: Number of bytes in signature field.

field.name: NoSides
field.description: Number of Side repeating group instances. ; Valid values:; 1 - one side; 2 - both sides

field.name: QueryOrdStatus
field.description: 0-Status for all orders 1-Status for orders which are not confirmed by the party 2-Status for all orders for the party 3-Cancelled 4-Modified 5-Partially Dealt 6-Fully Dealt 7-Pending

field.name: QueryStartNumber
field.description: Query Start Number FX Market Start number in results

field.name: QueryType
field.description: 0-RMB deal inquiry 1-Self Quote Inquiry 2-Self Deal Details Inquiry 3-Deal Details Inquiry by MBO User of Head Office 4-Limit Inquiry 5-Settlement Inquiry 6-Announcement Inquiry 7-Click in Negotiate Reject Ratio Inquiry 8-Ratio Inquiry 9-Collateral Inquiry 10-Benchmark Inquiry 11-Net Value Inquiry 12-Trading Fee Invoice Inquiry 13-Trading Fee Inquiry 14-ABS Information Inquiry 15-FX Deal inquery 16-FX IRS or CRS inquery 17-FX Broadcast Request 18-FX Price Data Full Image Refresh Request 19-FX Historical Data Retransmission Request 20-RMB quote inquiry 21-Data center inquery_database name 22-Data center inquery_database schema name 23-Data center inquery_database char 35-acter sets value 24-Data center inquery_database time 25-Data center inquery_database table name 26-Data center inquery_database view name 27-Data center inquery_database table DDL 28-Data center inquery_database view DDL 29-Data center inquery_database column data 30-Data center inquery_database table data 31-Unsettled positions inquery 32-Calculation agent inquery 33-Derivative limit inquery 34-Net total value of fund inquery 35-Trader privilege data inquery 36-FX Option inquery 37- Gold deal inquery

field.name: TradeTime
field.description: Time the transaction represented by this ExecutionReport occurred
